A Layer for creating images designed for and including the neutrino settop box software. It builds with current yocto poky release "Rocko" and probably also future releases. 

Lots of information has been taken from other layers or found elsewhere in the net. It contains recipes and settings for the "Opticum AX HD51 4K UHD" Settop Box  

This is published under the BSD-2-Clause License. You should find a copy of the license in your yocto/poky/meta/files/common-licenses folder

